{"tid":2184580,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Uber輸咗官司","createTime":"2020-09-01T15:39:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-02T03:30:08.000Z","uid":183453,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2c6f80a98d778d36d5a36662e1e6f26141c95ddf","tid":2184580,"uid":183453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T15:39:35.000Z","msg":"24名2018年被裁定非法載客取酬罪成的Uber司機，去年遭高等法院裁定上訴失敗，今日終院即日駁回上訴。任職Uber司機６年的Simon（化名）對裁決感到失望，「最可惜（政府）一路唔肯去傾點樣立法規管，等我哋呢班Uber司機名正言順去經營，我哋唔介意去接受規管，明白成本一定上升，要讀書、考牌」，他重申所有要求統統願意，但沒機會。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200901/YFCSZFGFXJCOTOOVDURZAIVGDY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200901%2FYFCSZFGFXJCOTOOVDURZAIVGDY%2F&d=H6IDb39AroI58YjM1eqeYbhWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=d34d93af\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200901%2FYFCSZFGFXJCOTOOVDURZAIVGDY%2F&h=c62effe6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200901/YFCSZFGFXJCOTOOVDURZAIVGDY/</a>"},{"pid":"9e642994c8cee089b1e8727cb3b0de2ef564d517","tid":2184580,"uid":34530,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T15:52:14.000Z","msg":"Uber 都唔係好人"},{"pid":"c2bceea117c1861bd0a798802af2e628e3180d89","tid":2184580,"uid":289396,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9e642994c8cee089b1e8727cb3b0de2ef564d517","tid":2184580,"uid":34530,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T15:52:14.000Z","msg":"Uber 都唔係好人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T03:12:12.000Z","msg":"都係爛仔"},{"pid":"87eabb91fe099a9ca9fd3b57534b9dc43afb5fae","tid":2184580,"uid":32028,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T03:13:04.000Z","msg":"比你入黎, 班狗官點樣引入DIDI呀"},{"pid":"8878bfe22434617ee0c3bcc4afcf11caa07313fa","tid":2184580,"uid":32028,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"87eabb91fe099a9ca9fd3b57534b9dc43afb5fae","tid":2184580,"uid":3